									<p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000;margin:10px 0 20px;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br /><br />This is a kind remider for your upcoming induction with Alliance Nursing.<br /><br />
Start time: {!b3o__Session_Invitation__c.Booking_Time_Local__c}<br />
End time: {!b3o__Session_Invitation__c.Booking_End_Time_Local__c}<br />
Message:{!b3o__Session__c.b3o__Booking_Confirmation_Message__c}<br />

<p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000;margin:10px 0 20px;">If you have any questions before the induction, please feel free to reach out on <a href="tel:1300034494">1300 034 494</a>. <br /><br />We are looking forward to hearing a bit more about you and your work experience!
									<br /><br />
									Kind regards,<br />
									Your team at Alliance Nursing</p>
